WEBVTT

1
00:00:57.590 --> 00:00:59.760 
游说的重点是洞察先机
Lobbying is about foresight.

2
00:01:01.850 --> 00:01:04.600 
预测对手招数
About anticipating your opponent's moves

3
00:01:05.230 --> 00:01:07.530 
然后设计对策
and devising countermeasures.

4
00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:14.000 
赢家永远比对手快一步
The winner plots one step ahead of the opposition,

5
00:01:15.590 --> 00:01:17.550 
当对方一掀底牌
and plays her trump card

6
00:01:18.670 --> 00:01:20.970 
就亮出王牌
just after they play theirs.

